{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode3C1H|ode', 'text' : 'Ode iii.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode3C1H|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 4.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode3C1H|melody', 'text' : 'Heirmos.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode3C1H|text', 'text' : 'Your Church rejoices in You, O Christ our God, and she cries out to You, * "You are my mighty strength, O Lord, * and You are my refuge and firm support."'}
