{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode3Kathisma1|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 4.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode3Kathisma1|melody', 'text' : 'Come quickly.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode3Kathisma1|text', 'text' : 'When Christ our Redeemer came, He did illumine all things, * renewing the world by His all-holy Spirit as God. * And souls are restored as well. * For now is consecrated * to the Lord's holy glory * a holy house and temple, wherein Christ our Lord and Savior * sanctifies the hearts of believers, * for the salvation of humanity.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode3KathismaT|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 4.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode3KathismaT|melody', 'text' : 'Come quickly.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode3KathismaT|text', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode4C1H|ode', 'text' : 'Ode iv.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode4C1H|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 4.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode4C1H|melody', 'text' : 'Heirmos.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode4C1H|text', 'text' : 'When the Church beheld You raised on the Cross unjustly, * You, the Sun of Righteousness, crucified for our sake, * she stood in her course and was amazed, and fittingly she cried out, * "Glory to Your power, O Lord my God."'}
{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode4C11|ode', 'text' : 'Ode iv.'}
