{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode7C1H|text', 'text' : 'Inside the furnace * in Persia, those descendants of Abraham * were with love and longing for godliness consumed * rather than by fire, and they cried, * "You are blessed, O Lord, * in the holy temple of Your glory."'}
