{'id_' : 'eu|consecration_en_US_dedes|euMA|Ode9C1H|text', 'text' : 'A cornerstone was cut out without hands * from a never-quarried mountain, * which prefigured you, holy Virgin. * The stone is Christ, who joined the disparate natures. * As we rejoice because of this, O Theotokos, we magnify you.'}
